title: The Complete Paintings of Manet (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The Complete Paintings of Manet
Harry N. Abrams | 1967 | ISBN: 0810955113 | English | 136 pages | PDF | 21.8 MB

Edouard Manet was one of the first artists - perhaps the first - whose work can even now be called "modern", and although he died in 1883 his art has remained contemporary in spirit. Indeed, young artists are again turning to his work for ideas and suggestions related to the integrity of the surface of the canvas, shallow spatial effects, and careful adjustment of color to shape and area
